	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I've been thinking about the map export. Making a simple 2D array is probably not what people need. It would be better to store lines and columns in DMA reads packets, so you can just set the DMA and go.<br /><br />What address inc setup to people use for these tasks?

		

		</td>
